<node id="&quot;COMPANY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Company is a business entity that is subject to certain conditions and events as outlined in the text."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company is a party to a Trademark Security Agreement with TriVascular, Inc. and the ABL Agent."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company is a reference to the main entity involved in the security agreements, likely a corporation or business entity."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company is the main entity whose business, results of operations, financial condition, assets, and liabilities are being evaluated for Material Adverse Effect."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company refers to the entity that is party to an agreement and has breached certain covenants or agreements, leading to potential termination of the agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company refers to the main entity and its subsidiaries involved in the transactions and agreements mentioned."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company refers to the organization receiving notice from the Supporting Lenders regarding the Restructuring."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-7a147f7c459c31c557d67f845e41b10e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d1cf7ab352d206df1f448fbd5cec8614&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-661ed10b78ea1234a9577552c2d9a9dc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb40ecdb4293f18153a89681852a4431&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39b66283140620725d611fdb3255464e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-086a5068bbc473cc9788d46b3609f100&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb778c7e1933191d37401574959679ec</data>
