  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Subsidiaries are affiliated companies of the Company, contributing to its overall business, results of operations, financial condition, assets, and liabilities."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are companies wholly owned or controlled by another company, and their representatives are included in the definition of 'Representatives'."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-7a147f7c459c31c557d67f845e41b10e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-661ed10b78ea1234a9577552c2d9a9dc</data>
