<node id="&quot;RESTRUCTURING&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Restructuring is a business process that the Company is undergoing, as indicated by the notice from the Supporting Lenders."&lt;SEP&gt;"Restructuring is the process of reorganizing the company's financial structure to improve its financial health."&lt;SEP&gt;"Restructuring refers to the process of reorganizing a company's financial structure, often in bankruptcy proceedings."&lt;SEP&gt;"Restructuring refers to the process of reorganizing the Debtors' operations or finances to improve their financial health."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-086a5068bbc473cc9788d46b3609f100&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7a147f7c459c31c557d67f845e41b10e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d490e69c3b4e25af388c35f68d9a7d0c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d1cf7ab352d206df1f448fbd5cec8614</data>
