<node id="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Supporting Lenders are financial institutions or entities supporting the restructuring process."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are financial institutions or entities that provide support to the Company under specific conditions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are parties to the agreement and must not be in material breach to allow certain conditions to remain uncured for three Business Days."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are the financial institutions providing support or loans to the Company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are the financial institutions that have agreed to support the restructuring plan and have the discretion to accept or reject the Post-Restructuring Insurance."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are the organizations providing notice to the Company regarding the Restructuring."</data>
