<node id="&quot;SINGERS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Singers are individuals who perform music and are part of the broader community of singers and music educators."&lt;SEP&gt;"Singers are individuals who perform music theater songs, ranging from beginners to professionals."&lt;SEP&gt;"Singers are individuals who perform vocal music, requiring proper warm-up to avoid injuries and improve performance."&lt;SEP&gt;"Singers are individuals who use neti pots regularly for nasal passage care and relief from allergies and chronic rhinosinusitis."&lt;SEP&gt;"Singers are performers who use their voices professionally, often requiring methods to maintain vocal health."&lt;SEP&gt;"Singers often use general teas to keep their throats healthy."&lt;SEP&gt;"Singers refer to individuals who perform singing as their profession, often in musical programs or performances."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c29545e3b52e75ce47be4109d5bcee9b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f2370a2f0c089c5553f3263304da90f0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1aad650700deaf8f43018f4278162b9a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d1cf7ab352d206df1f448fbd5cec8614&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-251f218c15356902066a23f0b89f1e4c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e33851bc0c2eecb00f46cce478ca9688&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-20739a7666e8702b6f28ac7666930a16</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 1}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 30}]</data>
</node>
