<node id="&quot;VOICE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Voice is the primary tool used in singing, encompassing both the speaking and singing registers."&lt;SEP&gt;"Voice refers to the sound produced by humans and animals, specifically in the context of singing and vocal effort."&lt;SEP&gt;"Voice refers to the sound produced by the vocal cords and amplified by the vocal tract."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-caaef3c4b63a56fa0f82f86264f30d0e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42e78df8d9ca72390c59785d98c0c246&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-20739a7666e8702b6f28ac7666930a16</data>
