<node id="&quot;LARYNX&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Larynx is the voice box that contains the vocal folds and is involved in the production of sound."&lt;SEP&gt;"The larynx is a part of the vocal system, likened to a knee in terms of its structure and function."&lt;SEP&gt;"The larynx, also known as the voice box, contains the vocal cords and is essential for voice production."</data>
