<node id="&quot;MALE BELT SINGING&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Male Belt Singing refers to a specific vocal technique used by male singers, particularly in musical theater, characterized by high passaggio and above pitches without pharyngeal expansion."&lt;SEP&gt;"Male Belt Singing refers to the technique used in male music theater singing where only the passaggio and above pitches are belted, maintaining a bright and speech-oriented sound without expanding the pharynx."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-770756a346b8a35323e1beddd87ca5e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e4031c3b36282f451cd6ca67a01df325</data>
