<node id="&quot;PASSAGGIO&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Passaggio is a term in vocal technique referring to the transition point in the voice, typically around the middle range."&lt;SEP&gt;"Passaggio is the point in a male singer's range where the voice transitions from chest voice to head voice, affecting the belting technique."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-770756a346b8a35323e1beddd87ca5e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e4031c3b36282f451cd6ca67a01df325</data>
