  <data key="d1">"Traditional Legit Sound is a type of legit singing that has the qualities of classical singing, featuring a darker quality and classical resonance."&lt;SEP&gt;"Traditional legit sound is a type of legit singing that closely follows the qualities of classical singing."</data>
