<node id="&quot;CONTEMPORARY LEGIT SOUND&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Contemporary Legit Sound is a type of legit singing that is head-voice dominant and more speech-oriented, resulting in a brighter and less classically resonant sound."&lt;SEP&gt;"Contemporary legit sound is a type of legit singing that incorporates modern elements while still maintaining classical qualities."&lt;SEP&gt;"Contemporary legit sound is the common sound used in modern Broadway musicals, contrasting with the classical style."</data>
