</node>
<node id="&quot;QUEEN CAGE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"OBJECT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Queen Cage is a structure used to place the queen bee within the hive for controlled breeding and management purposes."&lt;SEP&gt;"Queen cage is a container used to house the queen bee temporarily during hive inspections or relocations."&lt;SEP&gt;"queen cage is a temporary structure used to house a queen bee during the process of introducing her to a new colony."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-894b591a83b914f8f6e97ef8a4c38432&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-694253136982b7320b8099c8f3c852c7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ee60400c3602b512e18748159440dc7</data>
