</node>
<node id="&quot;BRIDGE COMB&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bridge comb is a type of comb that connects two frames, often forming a bridge-like structure, which can cause issues if not managed properly."&lt;SEP&gt;"bridge comb is a term used to describe comb that connects two frames, requiring the removal of both frames to address the issue."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-694253136982b7320b8099c8f3c852c7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ee60400c3602b512e18748159440dc7</data>
