<node id="&quot;WORKER BEES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Worker Bees are female bees that perform various tasks within the hive, such as caring for larvae and producing beeswax."&lt;SEP&gt;"Worker Bees are the female bees that perform various tasks within the hive, with an average lifespan of 4 to 5 weeks during the active season."&lt;SEP&gt;"Worker bees are female bees that perform various tasks such as foraging, building comb, and caring for the brood."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a5249d7cd72cb7719eac165e812133b7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-694253136982b7320b8099c8f3c852c7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-81ecf165e861b9b15f524411477efffe</data>
