<node id="&quot;NECTAR&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Nectar is a substance collected by workers for the colony, though drones cannot collect it."&lt;SEP&gt;"Nectar is a substance that bees collect and use to produce honey, and it is crucial for the bees to secrete additional wax and build comb."&lt;SEP&gt;"Nectar is a sweet liquid produced by flowers that bees collect to produce honey."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-31552e12186e5af657ecc15691569829&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cd3280f423032e87d8241124c131edc6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-894b591a83b914f8f6e97ef8a4c38432</data>
