</node>
<node id="&quot;HONEY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PRODUCT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Honey is a product mentioned in the context of nasal care."&lt;SEP&gt;"Honey is a sweet substance produced by bees from nectar and stored in the hive."&lt;SEP&gt;"Honey is recommended as an effective cough suppressant for children."&lt;SEP&gt;"Honey is stored by bees in the comb for food and future use."&lt;SEP&gt;"Honey is stored in the Honeycomb Cells and is a primary food source for the colony."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-894b591a83b914f8f6e97ef8a4c38432&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f2370a2f0c089c5553f3263304da90f0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-81ecf165e861b9b15f524411477efffe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a5249d7cd72cb7719eac165e812133b7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-251f218c15356902066a23f0b89f1e4c</data>
