  <data key="d0">"TECHNOLOGY"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bismuth Salts are used to make digestive tracts visible on X-rays due to their opacity to the rays."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bismuth salts are used in Cannon's experiments to make digestive tracts visible on X-rays due to their opacity to X-rays."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-65433026bd213bdc7f57a14af8a9a25f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b60c4a915bc63a445da3fc657d962949</data>
