</node>
<node id="&quot;1840S&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The 1840s is a period when the first burlesque musicals appeared in the United States.")</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9076ff576e2bf42857f37340864aa7f9</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;COLONIES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Colonies refers to the early American colonies that later formed the United States."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Colonies refer to the early American colonies, which is the historical context for the emergence of burlesque musicals.")</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9076ff576e2bf42857f37340864aa7f9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cd3280f423032e87d8241124c131edc6</data>
