  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Forage time is the period during which bees gather nectar and pollen, which is crucial for wax secretion and comb building."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-cd3280f423032e87d8241124c131edc6</data>
