<node id="&quot;ML-236B&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"TECHNOLOGY"</data>
  <data key="d1">"ML-236B is the initial name of the compound later known as compactin, which is a potent inhibitor of the reductase enzyme."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-6b282e8d4ca9bc6364047871f5ef3099</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;COMPACTIN&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"TECHNOLOGY"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Compactin is a compound discovered by Endo and patented by Sankyo, which later became part of the statin class of drugs."&lt;SEP&gt;"Compactin is a drug that showed promise in reducing cholesterol levels in various animal models but faced toxicity issues."&lt;SEP&gt;"Compactin is the final name of the compound ML-236B, which is a potent inhibitor of the reductase enzyme."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f25db7fec2da4d1e7ab8558cb54f8752&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ff6e96c06fdf561fcaa864617083bbab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6b282e8d4ca9bc6364047871f5ef3099</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;STATINS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"TECHNOLOGY"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Statins is a class of drugs developed from compactin, used to lower cholesterol and treat heart disease."&lt;SEP&gt;"Statins is a class of drugs that includes compactin and are used to lower cholesterol levels and reduce the risk of heart disease."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-ff6e96c06fdf561fcaa864617083bbab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6b282e8d4ca9bc6364047871f5ef3099</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;REDUCTASE INHIBITION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Reductase Inhibition is the mechanism by which compactin blocks the reductase enzyme, preventing it from functioning."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-6b282e8d4ca9bc6364047871f5ef3099</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ASPIRIN TABLET&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"TECHNOLOGY"</data>
  <data key="d1">"An aspirin tablet is used as a reference point for comparing the amount of the compound ML-236B, later known as compactin."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-6b282e8d4ca9bc6364047871f5ef3099</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SANKYO&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Sankyo is a pharmaceutical company that developed the drug compactin and encountered issues during clinical trials."&lt;SEP&gt;"Sankyo is a pharmaceutical company that supported the development of compactin and formed a project team to further develop the drug."&lt;SEP&gt;"Sankyo is a pharmaceutical company where Endo worked and published the discovery of compactin, a compound used in the development of statins."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-606dabdb846969f5b54692a4eb6683c6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f25db7fec2da4d1e7ab8558cb54f8752&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ff6e96c06fdf561fcaa864617083bbab</data>
</node>
