  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Officials are the authorities who reacted with alarm when William Henry Brown leased a performance space on Broadway."&lt;SEP&gt;"Officials are the governing bodies that initially tolerated Brown's success but later banned his performances."</data>
