</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ELTON&quot;" target="&quot;JULIAN HUXLEY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">38.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Julian Huxley invited Elton on the expedition and was impressed by his passion for natural history."&lt;SEP&gt;"Julian Huxley proposed for Elton to write a book on animal ecology, recognizing his expertise and original thinking."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4c3eb78a029c96288b495cbd85393985&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8cac479cb6cdd8c93500916fa7e3e364</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ELTON&quot;" target="&quot;_ANIMAL ECOLOGY_&quot;">
  <data key="d4">40.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Elton wrote the book _Animal Ecology_, which became a classic in terms of both style and substance."&lt;SEP&gt;"Elton wrote the book _Animal Ecology_, which was influenced by his extensive research and experience in the Arctic."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4c3eb78a029c96288b495cbd85393985</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
