  <data key="d4">26.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Elton documented his observations in a diary."&lt;SEP&gt;"Elton started a diary at age thirteen to record his wanderings and observations, indicating his dedication to documenting his experiences."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-8cac479cb6cdd8c93500916fa7e3e364&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-354a0d0ce64efc8fcedeea9bb16a6056</data>
