  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Mix register: a blend of light and heavy mechanism/head and chest register/mode one and two is an exercise for developing music theater singing."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-354a0d0ce64efc8fcedeea9bb16a6056</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;EXPEDITION&quot;" target="&quot;ISLAND&quot;">
  <data key="d4">20.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Expedition takes place on the Island, which is characterized by constant fog, sleet, and blizzards, with numerous lakes and flat terrain."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-20e38e48ffc37fb717229a5dc03ff3a9</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;EXPEDITION&quot;" target="&quot;BIRDERS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">24.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Birders are part of the larger Expedition, focusing on studying birdlife during the expedition."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Expedition includes birders who are focused on studying birdlife, including F.C.R. Jourdain and Elton."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-20e38e48ffc37fb717229a5dc03ff3a9</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;VOYAGE&quot;" target="&quot;SPITSBERGEN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The voyage to Spitsbergen was part of the expedition, lasting two months and involving Elton and the team."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-8cac479cb6cdd8c93500916fa7e3e364</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SPITSBERGEN&quot;" target="&quot;NORSK POLARINSTITUTTS LIBRARY, TROMSÖ, NORWAY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The library holds a photograph from the expedition to Spitsbergen, providing visual documentation of the event."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-8cac479cb6cdd8c93500916fa7e3e364</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SPITSBERGEN&quot;" target="&quot;TWO-MONTH VOYAGE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The two-month voyage took place to Spitsbergen, where the team conducted their research."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-8cac479cb6cdd8c93500916fa7e3e364</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SPITSBERGEN&quot;" target="&quot;ELEMENTARY SWISS CLIMBING&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Spitsbergen is a remote Arctic island where the expedition took place, not requiring the level of difficulty of elementary Swiss climbing."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-8cac479cb6cdd8c93500916fa7e3e364</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SPITSBERGEN&quot;" target="&quot;DIFFICULT MOUNTAINEERING&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Spitsbergen is a remote Arctic island where the expedition took place, not requiring the level of difficulty of difficult mountaineering."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-8cac479cb6cdd8c93500916fa7e3e364</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SPITSBERGEN&quot;" target="&quot;THE ISLAND&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The full team sails to Spitsbergen, about 120 miles to the north, after exploring the island."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-6dcaa3fb65de0bc40334b1db91763464</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;VINCENT SUMMERHAYES&quot;" target="&quot;ORNITHOLOGISTS GROUP&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Vincent Summerhayes is also part of the Ornithologists Group, working with Elton to survey plants and other animals."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-20e38e48ffc37fb717229a5dc03ff3a9</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;VINCENT SUMMERHAYES&quot;" target="&quot;F.C.R. JOURDAIN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"F.C.R. Jourdain is the leader of the expedition and commands Vincent Summerhayes along with Elton, but they follow Longstaff's advice instead."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-20e38e48ffc37fb717229a5dc03ff3a9</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;VINCENT SUMMERHAYES&quot;" target="&quot;LONGSTAFF&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Longstaff advises Vincent Summerhayes to ignore F.C.R. Jourdain's commands due to exhaustion concerns, and they follow this advice."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-20e38e48ffc37fb717229a5dc03ff3a9</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;WALRUS BAY&quot;" target="&quot;THE LANDING PARTY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
