  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The purpose of the first inspection is to check on the Queen Bee, ensuring she has been released."|&gt;</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-51f25ad8710ba3aff4a2bd9ece017fba</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
