  <data key="d6">chunk-694253136982b7320b8099c8f3c852c7</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEES&quot;" target="&quot;QUEEN CAGE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">23.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bees use the Queen Cage to house the queen for controlled breeding and management."&lt;SEP&gt;"Queen cage affects the behavior and roles of bees within the hive."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-894b591a83b914f8f6e97ef8a4c38432&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-694253136982b7320b8099c8f3c852c7</data>
