  <data key="d4">52.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bees collect nectar from flowers to produce honey and feed the colony."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bees collect nectar, which is crucial for the bees to secrete additional wax and build comb to construct their hives."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bees depend on nectar for the secretion of additional wax and building of comb, which is essential for hive construction."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-cd3280f423032e87d8241124c131edc6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-894b591a83b914f8f6e97ef8a4c38432</data>
