  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Cool Weather affects the Package Colony by reducing forage time and impacting the bees' ability to gather resources."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cool Weather impacts the Package Colony by reducing forage time and affecting the bees' ability to gather resources."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-a5249d7cd72cb7719eac165e812133b7</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PACKAGE COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;NECTAR FLOW&quot;">
  <data key="d4">12.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The absence of Nectar Flow complicates the situation for the Package Colony, as bees rely on nectar for food."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-a5249d7cd72cb7719eac165e812133b7</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PACKAGE COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;COMB&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The lack of Comb in the Package Colony hinders the storage of honey and pollen and the raising of brood."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-a5249d7cd72cb7719eac165e812133b7</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
