<edge source="&quot;GENETIC INFORMATION&quot;" target="&quot;ALTERATIONS IN GENES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">42.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Alterations in genes, as suggested by Rous, are not the primary cause of cancer according to Rowley's findings."|</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-d23a067b813d760afafa0dec63e383cc</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;GENETIC INFORMATION&quot;" target="&quot;CANCER-CAUSING AGENTS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">48.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Genetic information can include cancer-causing agents, as discussed in the context of oncogenes."|</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-d23a067b813d760afafa0dec63e383cc</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;GENETIC INFORMATION&quot;" target="&quot;SPECIFIC CHROMOSOMAL ABNORMALITIES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">54.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Specific chromosomal abnormalities are a form of genetic information that Rowley studied in leukemia patients."|</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-d23a067b813d760afafa0dec63e383cc</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;GENETIC INFORMATION&quot;" target="&quot;PHILADELPHIA CHROMOSOME&quot;">
  <data key="d4">54.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Philadelphia chromosome is a specific chromosomal abnormality that Rowley studied in Chronic Myelogenous Leukemia."|</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-d23a067b813d760afafa0dec63e383cc</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PROTECTIVE GEAR&quot;" target="&quot;VEIL&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The veil is part of the protective gear worn by the beekeeper during the inspection."|&gt;</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-51f25ad8710ba3aff4a2bd9ece017fba</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;POLLEN PELLETS&quot;" target="&quot;SIGN OF FORAGING&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Pollen pellets on the hind legs of bees indicate successful foraging."|&gt;</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-51f25ad8710ba3aff4a2bd9ece017fba</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;DAILY ROUTINE&quot;" target="&quot;NORMAL BEHAVIOR&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bees around the entrance look calm, following the daily routine."|&gt;</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-51f25ad8710ba3aff4a2bd9ece017fba</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;INITIAL CONDITION&quot;" target="&quot;PACKAGE INSTALLATION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The package installation is the initial condition for the inspection, assuming the queen will be released by the third day."|&gt;</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-51f25ad8710ba3aff4a2bd9ece017fba</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
